َ اِلَّا اَنْتَ الْبَارِئُ الْوَاحِدُ الْقَهَّارُ الَّذِيْ خَلَقَنِيْ وَلَمْ اَكُ شَيْئًا بِمَشِيَّتِهٖ وَاَرَانِيْ فِيْ نَفْسِيْ وَفِيْ كُلِّ شَيْ‌ءٍ مِنْ مَخْلُوْقَاتِهٖ وَصُنْعِهِ الدَّلَائِلَ الْبَيِّنَةَ النَّيِّرَةَ عَلٰى قُدْرَتِهِ الَّذِيْ فَرَضَ عَلَيَّ الصِّيَامَ تَعَبُّدًا يُصْلِحُ بِهٖ شَانِيْ وَيَغْسِلُ عَنِّيْ اَوْزَارِيْ وَيَذْكُرُنِيْ بِمَا لَهَوْتُ عَنْهُ مِنْ ذِكْرِهٖ وَيُوْجِبُ لِيَ الزُّلْفٰى بِطَاعَةِ اَمْرِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015425, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my God! O my Master! You are my Guardian! Please increase any good deeds that I may have done in the past and pleased You and forgive me if what I did caused Your Wrath O my God! Grant me more of the guidance that You have and enable me to force myself to return to what is in agreement with Your Will Choose what would lead to Your servants prosperity by Your Obedience and save him from wretchedness due to Your Disobedience so that he may prosper amongst the Immaculate Ones and be saved amongst those whose deeds are accepted and be in the company of those who prosper those who have no fear nor any grief Please bestow blessings on Muhammad and his Progeny and may His peace be on them plentifully.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SAYYADI ANTA MAWLAA-YA IN KUNTA JUDTA A’LAIY-YA BE-SAALE-HIN FEE-MAA MAZAA MIN-HUR TAZEE-TAHU FA-ZIDNEE WA IN KUN-TAQ RAFTA MAA AS-KHATA-KA FA-AQIL-NEE. ALLAAHUMMA MALLIK-NEE MIN NAFSEE FIL HODAA MAA ANTA LAHU AM-LAKO WA QADDIR-NEE MENAL O’DOO-LE BE-HAA ILAA ERAA-DATEKA A’LAA MAA ANTA A’LAIY-HE AQ-DARO WA KUN MUKH-TAA-RAN LE-A’B-DEKA MAA YUS-E’DOHU BE-TAA-A’TE-KA WA TAJANNO-BE-HISH SHIQ-WATA BE-MA’SE-YATE-KA HATTAA YAKOO-ZA FIL MA’SOO-MEENA WA YAN-JOWA FIL MAQBOO-LEENA WA YO-RAAFE-QAL FAAA-E-ZEE-NAL LAZEENA LAA KHAW-FOON A’LAIY-HIM WA LAA HUM YAH-ZANOO-NA WA SALLAL-LAAHO A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE-HI WA SALLAMA TASLEE-MAN KASEE-RAN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ سَيِّدِيْ اَنْتَ مَوْلَايَ اِنْ كُنْتَ جُدْتَ عَلَيَّ بِصَالِحٍ فِيْمَا مَضٰى مِنْهُ ارْتَضَيْتَهٗ فَزِدْنِيْ وَاِنْ كُنْتَ اقْتَرَفْتَ مَا اَسْخَطَكَ فَاَقِلْنِيْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ مَلِّكْنِيْ مِنْ نَفْسِيْ فِي الْهُدٰى مَا اَنْتَ لَهٗ اَمْلَكُ وَقَدِّرْنِيْ مِنَ الْعُدُوْلِ بِهَا اِلٰى اِرَادَتِكَ عَلٰى مَا اَنْتَ عَلَيْهِ اَقْدَرُ وَكُنْ مُخْتَارًا لِعَبْدِكَ مَا يُسْعِدُهٗ بِطَاعَتِكَ وَتَجَنُّبِهِ الشِّقْوَةَ بِمَعْصِيَتِكَ حَتّٰى يَفُوْزَ فِي الْمَعْصُوْمِيْنَ وَيَنْجُوَ فِي الْمَقْبُوْلِيْنَ وَيُرَافِقَ الْفَاۗئِزِيْنَ الَّذِيْنَ‌ لَا خَوْفٌ عَلَيْهِمْ وَلَا هُمْ يَحْزَنُوْنَ‌ وَصَلَّى اللهُ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِهٖ وَسَلَّمَ تَسْلِيْمًا كَثِيْرًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12"